<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, January 27 (Xinhua) -- French President Jacques Chirac
Tuesday called for an enlargement of the United Nations "Oil for
Food" program with Iraq during his talks with United Nations
Secretary General Kofi Annan in Paris.
</P>
<P>
The presidential spokeswoman Catherine Colonna said that Chirac
stressed the "usefulness" for an expanding of the U.N. Security
