greetings to my teacher on the first day of the Lunar New Year,"
said one middle school student.
</P>
<P>
Workers on the Three Gorges Dam Project marked the Lunar New
Year with yet another hard day at work. One official noted that
many of the workers have spent six festivals at construction
sites since the beginning of the project.
</P>
<P>
Just as most Chinese cities, Zhengzhou in Henan Province and
the Hebei city of Shijiazhuang were both bedecked with thousands
of red lanterns and colored lights which added jubilant atmosphere
to the festival.
</P>
<P>
Residents in Shandong Province, east China, enjoy the festival
by attending performances or temple fairs. However, many people
working in the service sector, including electric power and water
supply departments and department stores, continue to perform
their duties to ensure local residents have a happy holiday
season.
</P>
