was good news for the economy and if it continued would also keep
interest rates low.
</P>
<P>
The Australian dollar finished the local session Wednesday at
85.28 Japanese yen, from 84.47 yen in Sydney Tuesday and at 1.2152
German marks from 1.1904 marks.  
