<P>
He said he decided to resign because he felt responsible for
the bomb attack by the Liberation Tigers of Tamil Eelam (LTTE) in
Kandy Sunday morning.
</P>
<P>
A truck bomb exploded by LTTE rebels killed 16 people and
damaged the holiest Buddhist shrine, the Dalada Maligawa (Tooth
Relic Temple), arousing a nation-wide anger against the
organization and serious criticism on security lapse.
</P>
<P>
The main opposition, the United National Party, has request the
minister to step down from his post following the incident.
</P>
<P>
It's not clear whether the president has accepted the
resignation or not.  
</P>
