<HEADLINE> Thailand, South Korea Wins Matches in King's Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, January 27 (Xinhua) -- Host Thailand struck a
spectacular free kick in the first half to upset European
powerhouse Denmark in their opening game of the 29th King's Cup
soccer tournament here on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
